{
  "stem": "5758.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we-- ah, by that time, naturally, France was occupied by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because Belgium was occupied on the 10th.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "France was occupied by the 14th of-- of May.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] however, if you remember, the French occupied the northern part, and Limoges was in the unoccupied zone.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we felt quite safe, but I couldn't really do anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a Jewish organization there, but [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we-- there was a-- we ate in the-- in the community center.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And again, we were given some pocket money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I wanted to play music.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was unable to get hold of a cello, because I left the cello in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I couldn't carry it with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I said to my cousin-- to my uncle, said, look, I want to go and retrieve my cello that I had in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, you must be mad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You go in that-- Into the occupied zone?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, look, I can earn my living here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'll come back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had a bit of money saved up, and they gave me some money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I took the train, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] went to the border of the occupied zone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went illegally across there into the occupied zone, went to the next town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Took the train, went to-- to Belgium, you know, that-- to find the-- the cello and maybe clothes, because I hardly-- I didn't have any clothes whatsoever because everything was left there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I found a sympathetic Belgium who took me to [NON-ENGLISH] by car.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I looked around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The place was completely destroyed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Every-- everything was ransacked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I couldn't find anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no cello, no clothes, no-- even barracks were destroyed.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
